we are sometimes subject to fiscal funding clauses in our software licensing transactions with the united states government and its agencies 
such clauses generally provide that the license is cancelable if the legislature or funding authority does not appropriate the funds necessary for the governmental unit to fulfill its obligations under the licensing arrangement 
